data.description: Welcome to 112 Mallard Hill, nestled in the charming community of The Meadows. This exquisite property boasts over 2700 square feet of living space on a generous .36-acre lot. The welcoming front porch adorned with rocking chairs invites you to relax and enjoy the serene surroundings. Step into the grandeur of a 2-story living room and foyer, leading to a well-appointed kitchen with a central island, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. With 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, including a main-level bedroom and bath, this home offers flexibility and convenience. The owner's suite on the main level features dual closets, a separate shower, and a luxurious tub. Upstairs, discover three more bedrooms, an additional full bath, and a versatile office space. Two covered decks provide ideal outdoor spaces, while a 2-car garage adds practicality. Noteworthy is the brand new roof, ensuring long-lasting quality. This residence harmoniously combines style, functionality, and comfort, creating a haven to call home.
